Description: Thank you for visiting our ebay store! Live life easier with reisenthel! Big work of art, small format: Just fold it 3 times and it fits into its own outer pocket. With its foldable wheels, the foldabletrolley from reisenthel is packed away in a jiffy and quickly ready for use again, as soon as it is needed. Whether a trip to the craft store, an early morning at the farmer's market or simply transporting your lunch to and from the office, the trolleybag is designed for ultimate style, function and portability. A convenient accessory in an elegant baroque print, mix and match this trolleybag with other reisenthel products to complete all of your travel and toting needs. The reisenthel foldabletrolley is made from easy-to-clean, premium quality, water-repellent polyester and measures 11-1/2-inches long by 10-3/4-inches wide by 26-inches high when fully expanded. Equipped with a foldable design, the trolleybag is able to compact into an ultra portable size of 11-1/2-inches by 2-1/2-inches by 9-3/4-inches. Its sturdy edge, bottom backboard provides protection while its firm dimensional base plate provides stability. Featuring a roomy main compartment with a press-stud closure and Velcro handgrip handles, the foldabletrolley is a sturdy, comfortable and practical addition to simplify every day life. Since 1971, reisenthel has been synonymous with innovative ideas, functional design and delightful everyday helpers. They aim for simplicity making each product straightforward and uncomplicated.
